        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】Realme 推出可拆換鏡頭概念智能電話，一吋 sensor、人像長焦兼備</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/realme-ultra/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=realme-ultra</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/realme-ultra/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 11:18:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MWC2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[realme Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295212</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>隨著科技不斷進步，智慧型手機攝影迎來新里程碑。realme 在 2025 年世界流動通信大會（MWC 2025）上，首次展示其可拆換鏡頭概念機。這款創新產品配備 1 吋 Sony 訂製感光元件及獨特鏡頭接口設計，讓用戶可直接安裝專業單眼鏡頭，革新手機拍攝體驗。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295230" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370544-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370544-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370544.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配備一吋 Sensor</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295231" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370559-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370559-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370559.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>這款概念機名為 ULTRA，內置 1 吋影像感測器，並配備兩款專業鏡頭：73mm 人像鏡頭及 234mm 長焦鏡頭，實現 10 倍光學變焦。從官方影片可見，產品包裝盒分為手機與鏡頭兩部分，設計新穎。其光學畫質媲美單眼相機，無論細膩景深或遠距離拍攝，均令人耳目一新。據 IT 之家報導，realme 強調這是品牌首款支援 10 倍光學變焦的機型，技術突破備受矚目。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370531-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370531-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030370531.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371032-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371032-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371032.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295233" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371044-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371044-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371044.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295234" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371054-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371054-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030371054.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>消息一出，立即引起網民熱議。X 用戶 Shindensha 表示：「realme 這款機感覺真係可以隨需裝鏡頭，相當有趣，沒想到這種手機會出自 realme。」</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">realmeのやつ、なんか本當に交換式というか、交換式というよりはレンズが付屬していて、必要に応じて取付できる感じに見えるな<br />
ええめっちゃ面白いと思うけど、こういうスマホがrealmeから出ることが衝撃ですよ。</p><p>— はるつばめ (@Shindensha) <a href="https://twitter.com/Shindensha/status/1894735203337445598?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 26, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br />
另有網民 MItu8_san 則關注技術細節：「如果是 1 吋感測器加可換鏡頭，手機厚度會否成問題？」此外小米早於 2022 年推出 12S Ultra 概念機，支援 Leica M 系列鏡頭；而今年小米再推磁吸式模組光學系統，顯示手機攝影技術競爭日趨激烈。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">Realme Ultraがレンズ交換式って初出どこなん&#8230;？<br />
ティザー畫像から類推するに中央の窪みは単なるペリスコープでもし1インチセンサーならイヤでもテレセントリック性悪化するでしょ<br />
それかフランジバック分稼いでるにしてもスマホの筐體じゃねえ</p><p>— みつば (@MItu8_san) <a href="https://twitter.com/MItu8_san/status/1895689309132636663?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 1, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>realme 憑藉可拆換鏡頭概念機及 14 Pro 系列，在 MWC 2025 上展現技術實力與市場野心。這款手機若順利推出市場，可能掀起手機攝影新浪潮。</p><p>資料來源：IT 之家</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
