        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】小米研發磁吸 M4/3 鏡頭模組，1 億像素、等效 35 mm f/1.4</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/xiaomi-unveils-ambitious-modular-phone-concept-with-lens-attachment/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xiaomi-unveils-ambitious-modular-phone-concept-with-lens-attachment</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/xiaomi-unveils-ambitious-modular-phone-concept-with-lens-attachment/mobile-phone/phone-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:59:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手機配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[m43]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MWC2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米模塊光學系統]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295203</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米於 2025 年 MWC 世界移動通訊大會上展示了一項全新概念產品——「小米模塊光學系統」，系統透過磁吸式設計，將配備 1 億像素 M4/3 感光器及 35mm f/1.4 定焦鏡頭的模組與手機連接，提升手機攝影畫質及功能。該技術利用高速觸點傳輸影像數據，實現相機光學與手機計算能力的深度結合。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/f91feba0f7fd11efb7ff-694x365.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/f91feba0f7fd11efb7ff-694x365.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/f91feba0f7fd11efb7ff.jpeg 959w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295208" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295209" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「小米模塊光學系統」採用磁吸觸點技術，模組內置 1 億像素 M4/3 感光器及 f/1.4 大光圈定焦鏡頭，支援 RAW 格式拍攝，並配備自動對焦馬達及手動對焦環。據外媒報導，該系統使用小米獨有的 LaserLink 技術，數據傳輸速度極快，與手機內置相機體驗相近。產品設計靈感或源於 Sony QX 系列及 Motorola Moto Mods，但小米在穩定性及畫質上作出顯著改進。X 網民 real_veryjack 表示：「M43 畫幅加 f1.4 光圈，體積小巧，對愛好輕便設備的人來説吸引力很大。」</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="zh">小米最近公佈的一個概念產品 &#8212; 外掛鏡頭，真的是太吸引我了🤩。M43 畫幅，f1.4 的光圈（相當於全畫幅的 f2.8），等效 35mm 焦段📷。體積只有一個餅乾鏡頭大小，比口袋裏塞一個卡片機還要方便。對於喜歡小巧產品的人來説，根本把持不住，期待產品落地。<a href="https://t.co/QSzO1gPpMm">https://t.co/QSzO1gPpMm</a></p><p>— 阿杰 Jack (@real_veryjack) <a href="https://twitter.com/real_veryjack/status/1896469508237447503?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 3, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>回顧過去，Sony 於 2013 年推出 QX 系列鏡頭相機，雖有 1 寸感光器及 10X 光學變焦，但因 Wi-Fi 連線不穩而失敗。2016 年 Motorola 與 Hasselblad 合作的 Moto Mods True Zoom 則配備 1/2.3 寸感光器及氙氣閃燈，卻因畫質提升有限未獲成功。小米的方案則以更大感光器及觸點傳輸技術，試圖突破瓶頸。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/xiaomimodularoptical-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>小米這款概念產品展現了手機攝影的新可能性，未來的發展或取決於市場反饋及技術成熟度。若成功量產，或許能開創手機外接光學模組的新生態，改變消費者對手機攝影的認知。業界預測小米於後續發佈會透露更多計劃。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_97130"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BBuvc_K8tDg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://www.androidauthority.com/xiaomi-concept-modular-phone-attachable-lens-3531335/">Android Authority</a>、<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E9%A0%90%E7%A0%94%E7%A3%81%E5%90%B8-m43-%E5%AE%9A%E7%84%A6%E6%A8%A1%E7%B5%84%E5%85%89%E5%AD%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%87%E7%9B%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%85%89%E5%AD%B8%E8%88%87%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%AE%97%E5%8A%9B%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88%E3%80%8D-071605623.html">Yahoo</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
