        <item>
            <title>一啪上電腦即變三屏幕   Lenovo Magic Bay Dual Display 模組化概念配件發表</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/lenovo-magic-bay-dual-display/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-magic-bay-dual-display</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/lenovo-magic-bay-dual-display/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 08:55:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lenovo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Magic Bay Dual Display]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295188</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p data-start="40" data-end="160">Lenovo 於 2025 年世界流動通訊大會（MWC 2025）正式發表一款嶄新模組化概念，讓筆電透過 Magic Bay 生態系統擴充成三屏幕便攜式工作站。這個產品針對專業用戶，為經常需要處理多任務的商務人士提供更高效的工作體驗。</p><p data-start="40" data-end="160"><h3 data-start="162" data-end="195"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vj4qslplhuf9rlbjtesb-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vj4qslplhuf9rlbjtesb-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vj4qslplhuf9rlbjtesb.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3 data-start="162" data-end="195"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02958jpg-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02958jpg-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02958jpg.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p data-start="196" data-end="363">Lenovo 於 ThinkBook 16p Gen 6 筆電上推出 Magic Bay 系列模組化配件。其中 <strong data-start="262" data-end="291">Magic Bay Dual Display 概念產品</strong> 讓用戶能額外添加兩塊 13.3 吋副屏幕，變成一個完整的三屏幕工作站，提升數據視覺化、內容編輯及協作效率，無需外接傳統顯示器即可實現多工處理。</p><p data-start="196" data-end="363"><p data-start="365" data-end="497">除了三屏幕配置，Lenovo 亦展示 <strong data-start="384" data-end="412">Magic Bay 2nd Display 概念</strong>，這是一款 8 吋小型副屏幕，可作為 AI 儀錶板，提供即時存取生產力工具、訊息應用程式及 AI 生成數據分析，確保用戶隨時掌握關鍵資訊，特別適合需要靈活工作的專業人士。</p><p data-start="365" data-end="497"><p data-start="521" data-end="676">Lenovo 於 MWC 2025 前夕率先展示該技術，Magic Bay Dual Display 概念讓筆電能夠透過磁吸式基座擴展為三屏幕配置，當用戶將副屏幕安裝於 ThinkBook 16p Gen 6，系統會自動識別，無需額外設置即可運行。此設計簡化了以往筆電使用多屏幕的繁瑣步驟，讓移動辦公更具彈性。</p><p data-start="521" data-end="676"><h3 data-start="162" data-end="195"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ek1h64dscf2784jpg-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ek1h64dscf2784jpg-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ek1h64dscf2784jpg.jpg 829w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p data-start="521" data-end="676"><p data-start="678" data-end="797">根據《Laptop Mag》預覽報導，這套顯示技術運作流暢，屏幕可摺疊收納於筆電背部，使用時迅速展開並立即連接。對於經常攜帶設備出差的專業人士，這種便攜式三屏幕設計能夠大幅提升工作效率，無論是處理數據、視訊會議還是內容編輯，皆能流暢運行。</p><p data-start="678" data-end="797"><p data-start="825" data-end="956">資料來源：<a href="https://news.lenovo.com/pressroom/press-releases/advancing-ai-powered-business-computing-thinkpad-thinkbook-concept-devices/">Lenovo</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
